0&0&1
\end{bmatrix}| &= \frac{1}{2}\left|\frac{1}{8}\right| = \frac{1}{16}.
\end{align*}

Step 3: The area of the triangle with vertices $(0,0,1),$ $\left(0,\frac 14,0\right),$ and $(0,0,\frac 15)$ is given by:

